{"tid":794271,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[讚揚]十分感謝各環保人士嘅爸爸媽媽","createTime":"2018-08-26T06:09:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-26T06:27:24.000Z","uid":4213,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8f5f65b9723fc3ce7e321194b2241cadab9c0245","tid":794271,"uid":4213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T06:09:01.000Z","msg":"當世界上所有人都只會消耗地球嘅資源<br />\n<br />\n環保人士嘅爸爸媽媽就先做好身教<br />\n當年無套中出 生咗各位環保人士出來保護地球<br />\n環保嘅路好漫長 <br />\n昨日廢膠袋  今日廢飲管 明日廢各式膠製品<br />\n只要堅持 地球伯伯總係會康復<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但屌你地班仆街<br />\n你地生埋成堆垃圾環保撚出來<br />\n呢班偽善環保撚點撚樣回收啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"019833cb8f3cb392a8cb7bfd173280945b60b027","tid":794271,"uid":82482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T06:27:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}